The <a href="/site/apidocs/org/apache/juneau/marshall/json/JcsSerializer.html" target="_blank">JcsSerializer</a> converts POJOs to canonical JSON. The <a href="/site/apidocs/org/apache/juneau/marshall/marshaller/Jcs.html" target="_blank">Jcs</a> marshaller pairs it with <a href="/site/apidocs/org/apache/juneau/marshall/json/JsonParser.html" target="_blank">JsonParser</a> for full round-trip support (JCS output is valid JSON).

