        @Header(
            name="api_key",
            description="Security API key",
            required=true,
            example="foobar"
        )
        String apiKey,
        @Path(
            name="petId",
            description="Pet id to delete",
            example="123"
        )
        long petId
    ) throws IdNotFound, NotAcceptable;

    ...
```

